772
01:01:18,369 --> 01:01:21,043
<i>Often I shivered as if inside an ice slab.</i>

773
01:01:21,163 --> 01:01:23,204
<i>Biting cold I couldn't bear.</i>

774
01:01:24,845 --> 01:01:27,086
