Return that lost sleep.

909
01:12:56,600 --> 01:12:59,678
I lost Ruby. Can you get her back?

910
01:13:00,038 --> 01:13:02,881
My sisters stopped smiling.
Return that smile.

911
01:13:02,959 --> 01:13:05,040
Can you? You peddler!

912
01:13:32,682 --> 01:13:35,121
My real gods.

913
01:13:36,081 --> 01:13:36,926
And one more.

914
01:13:40,285 --> 01:13:42,004
Lord Ganesha, MD.

915
01:13:42,886 --> 01:13:44,722
He's lived with me in prison, too.

916
01:13:50,485 --> 01:13:51,608
You're crying?

917
01:13:52,844 --> 01:13:54,169
Was the story so bad?

918
01:13:56,177 --> 01:13:57,810
Will you write it?

919
